### Suisho5 (水匠5) — Evaluation function

- Author: たややん (Tayayan, <https://x.com/tayayan_ts>)
- Distribution:
  <https://github.com/yaneurao/YaneuraOu/releases/tag/suisho5>
- License: Apache License, Version 2.0
- The Suisho5 evaluation function is **not redistributed in this
  repository**. It is fetched on demand by
  `evals/baseline/suisho5/fetch.ps1` from the official YaneuraOu
  release page.
- Optimal `FV_SCALE` for Suisho5 is `24`.

## Acknowledgments

This project would not exist without the decades of work by the
computer shogi community in Japan. In particular, the open-source
